<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Architecture {{ env_label }} - TP IaC</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: {{ page_color | default('#f0f2f5') }};
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 2rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 5px solid #2c3e50;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #95a5a6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="badge" style="background-color: {{ page_color }};">
            Environnement : {{ env_label }}
        </div>
        
        <h1>Dashboard Infrastructure</h1>

        <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Serveur Web :</span> 
                <code>{{ ansible_host }}</code>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Base de Données :</span> 
                <code>{{ hostvars[groups['dbservers'][0]]['ansible_host'] }}</code>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>Le flux est sécurisé via <strong>HTTPS</strong> et le pare-feu <strong>UFW</strong> restreint les accès.</p>

        <footer>
            Déployé automatiquement par Terraform & Ansible
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
